advised clients in the global retail and consumer segments he also has worked extensively with jbs the company said colaco earned an mba from the univ of chicago booth school of business “russ brings strong financial expertise and a broadbased strategic perspective to jbs” wesley batista ceo said in a statement “he will play an important leadership role as we seek to fully implement our global strategy” in may jbs sa the world’s largest meatpacker announced plans to fold its international businesses and its seara alimentos chicken processing business into jbs foods international and change jbs sa to jbs brasil jbs brasil will hold the company’s brazilian beef biodiesel collagen and carrier businesses along with its global leather business related articles jbs utah beef complex fully operational jbs to spin off international business jbs announces reorganization read more global  comment on this article we welcome your thoughtful comments please comply with our community rules your name name is required your email address email address is required add your comment the views expressed in the comments section of meat and poultry news do not reflect those of meat and poultry news or its parent company sosland publishing co kansas city mo concern regarding a specific comment may be registered with the editor by clicking the report abuse link enter code as it is shown required please enter code code does not match news global business trends regulatory food safety new technology bacon business product formulation archive most popular read shared comments usda develops food safety tool for meat inspectors ok foods to acquire albertville quality foods officials confirm  cases in chipotle illness outbreak amazon files for meal kit trademark possible extraneous material causes hot dog recall  more  usda develops food safety tool for meat inspectors amazon files for meal kit trademark from bowls to burritos formulating breakfast meats atypical bse found in alabama cow looking 